 Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] `ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml` compiles a binary named `ralph-burning` (edition 2021, Rust stable)\n- [ ] Dependencies include at minimum: `clap` (derive), `serde`/`serde_json`, `toml`/`toml_edit`, `thiserror`, `chrono`, and `tokio` (rt-multi-thread)\n- [ ] Source tree contains the bounded-context folder skeleton: `src/contexts/{workspace_governance, project_run_record, workflow_composition, agent_execution, requirements_drafting, automation_runtime, conformance_spec}/mod.rs` plus `src/adapters/mod.rs` and `src/shared/mod.rs`\n- [ ] Domain model types defined in `src/shared/domain.rs` (or equivalent shared module): `FlowPreset` enum (`Standard`, `QuickDev`, `DocsChange`, `CiImprovement`), `StageId` enum with all stages from all four presets, `StageCursor` struct (stage, cycle, attempt, completion_round), `ProjectId`, `RunId`, `WorkspaceConfig` struct\n- [ ] Four built-in flow presets are defined in `src/contexts/workflow_composition/` with their exact stage sequences as specified in the master prompt section 9\n- [ ] `ralph-burning init` creates `.ralph-burning/workspace.toml` with sensible defaults (version field, created timestamp) and the required subdirectory stubs (`projects/`, `requirements/`, `daemon/tasks/`, `daemon/leases/`)\n- [ ] `ralph-burning init` on an already-initialized workspace prints an error message and exits non-zero (no implicit re-init)\n- [ ] `ralph-burning flow list` prints all four preset names with a short description\n- [ ] `ralph-burning flow show <flow-id>` prints the ordered stage list, validation profile defaults (final review enabled/disabled), and stage count for the given preset\n- [ ] `ralph-burning flow show` with an invalid flow-id exits non-zero with a clear error\n- [ ] CLI top-level uses `clap` subcommand routing with placeholder subcommand stubs for all v1 commands (config, project, run, requirements, daemon, conformance) that print \"not yet implemented\" and exit non-zero\n- [ ] `tests/conformance/features/workspace_init.feature` contains Gherkin scenarios: init fresh workspace, init already-initialized workspace, init verifies directory structure\n- [ ] `tests/conformance/features/flow_discovery.feature` contains Gherkin scenarios: list all presets, show each preset, show invalid preset\n- [ ] Unit tests exist for: flow preset stage ordering, stage cursor construction invariants (monotonic cycle/completion round), workspace config serialization round-trip\n- [ ] `cargo build` succeeds with no warnings; `cargo test` passes all tests\n- [ ] `cargo clippy` reports no warnings\n\n## Files to Modify/Create\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/Cargo.toml` — new crate manifest with binary target and dependencies\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/main.rs` — async entry point, tracing init, clap CLI dispatch\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/lib.rs` — public module re-exports\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/mod.rs` — top-level clap `Cli` struct with all subcommand groups (stubs for unimplemented ones)\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/init.rs` — `ralph-burning init` implementation\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/flow.rs` — `ralph-burning flow list` and `flow show` implementation\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/config.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/project.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/run.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/requirements.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/conformance.rs` — placeholder stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/mod.rs` — shared module root\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/domain.rs` — core domain types (FlowPreset, StageId, StageCursor, ProjectId, RunId, WorkspaceConfig)\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/shared/error.rs` — shared error types using `thiserror`\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/workspace_governance/mod.rs` — workspace init logic, config loading, workspace version check\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/workflow_composition/mod.rs` — flow preset registry, stage sequence definitions\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/project_run_record/mod.rs` — module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/agent_execution/mod.rs` — module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/requirements_drafting/mod.rs` — module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/mod.rs` — module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/conformance_spec/mod.rs` — module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/mod.rs` — adapter module stub\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/fs.rs` — filesystem adapter for workspace creation (ports/adapters boundary)\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/workspace_init.feature` — Gherkin scenarios for init\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/flow_discovery.feature` — Gherkin scenarios for flow commands\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/domain_test.rs` — unit tests for domain types\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/flow_preset_test.rs` — unit tests for flow preset definitions\n- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/workspace_test.rs` — unit tests for workspace config serialization\n\n## Dependencies\n- Requires: none (first slice)\n- Blocks: slice 2 (flow preset definitions + stage contracts + renderer contracts), slice 3 (workspace governance effective config), slice 4 (project/run canonical store)\n\n---\n","numLines":69,"startLine":1,"totalLines":69}}}
